page.title: 10A DAY IN MY LIFE
page.content: On{Saturday}we went to the doctors Then went to{Bury}to get some Clothes Afer that we went to{Asda}for some food then went home and had some Dinner,we had egg,bacon,beans,fried bread and Mushrooms mum and Paul had ice_cream for afters.The we did the pots and when we had finished. We went to Gateshead for the week end in our car.It was 7:50 when we got there we had a few sandwiches for tea and a drink of juice,I watched a film and went to bed.Sunday was a christning}of baby Louise.She was quiet compered to the other children.After that we went to Aunty Joans and had some food.I had tuna sandwiches,salmon sandwiches,a few pickle onions and trifle.We played hide_and_seek untill it was time to go home.
